data.chText: 找出…的准确位置；确定…的准确地点
data.enText: to find the exact position of sb/sth

data.chText: 机修工立即找到了出故障的地方。
data.enText: The mechanic located the fault immediately.

data.chText: 救援飞机正在努力查明失踪水手的下落。
data.enText: Rescue planes are trying to locate the missing sailors.
to put or build sth in a particular place

data.chText: 他们把总部设在了斯温登。
data.enText: They located their headquarters in Swindon.
to start a business in a particular place

data.chText: 在农村地区创办企业享有税收减免。
data.enText: There are tax breaks for businesses that locate in rural areas.

simple_means.memory_skill: loc 地方 + ate 表动词 → 坐落，位于

tr: take up residence and become established
example: The immigrants settled in the Midwest
Can you locate your cousins in the Midwest?
The company located some of their agents in Los Angeles

tr: determine or indicate the place, site, or limits of, as if by an instrument or by a survey
example: Our sense of sight enables us to locate objects in space
Locate the boundaries of the property

value.def: If you locate something or someone, you find out where they are.

example.ex: The scientists want to locate the position of the gene on a chromosome...
example.tran: 科学家们希望找出该基因在染色体中的位置。

example.ex: We've  simply been unable to locate him.
example.tran: 我们就是没办法找到他。

value.def: If you locate something in a particular place, you put it there or build it there.

example.ex: Atlanta was voted the best city in which to locate a business by more than 400 chief executives...
example.tran: 逾400名行政总裁投票推选亚特兰大为最适宜开办公司的城市。

example.ex: Tudor Court represents your opportunity to locate  at the heart of the new Birmingham.
example.tran: 都铎宛，您在新伯明翰中心区置业的好机会。

value.def: If you locate in a particular place, you move there or open a business there.

example.ex: ...tax breaks for businesses that locate in run-down neighbor-hoods.
example.tran: 针对开办在老旧街区的商户的减税措施

partsOfSpeech.dec: al 加强 + loc 地方 + ate 做，造成，使… → 不断往地方送 → 分配〔东西〕
col 共同 + loc 地方 + ate 表动词 → 放在同一地方 → 并列放置
dis 不，没有 + loc 地方 + ate 做，造成，使… → 没在位置上 → 移位
echo 回声 + location 位置 → 回声定位法
partsOfSpeech.d: 回声定位能力；回声定位法

partsOfSpeech.dec: loc 地方 + al …的 → 地方的；局部的
local 地方的；局部的 + ism …主义 → 地方主义
local 地方的；局部的 + ity 具备某种性质，状况 → 位置，所在地
loc 地方 + ate 做，造成，使… → 坐落，位于
loco 地方 + mot 动 + ion 表动作 → 从一个地方到另一个地方 → 运动
loco 地方 + mot 动 + ive 表物 → 从一个地方跑到另一个地方的东西 → 火车头
loc 地方 + us 表名词，用于科学术语 → 地点，所在地
re 重新 + locate 坐落，位于 → 重新定位
